caller_intent: The caller requested a quote for homeowners insurance and indicated they do not currently have any policies with Alliance Insurance.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the request for a homeowners insurance quote.
Agent asked if the caller currently has policies with Alliance Insurance (answered 'no').
Agent offered to transfer the caller to an agent and asked them to hold.
knowledge_required: Process for transferring calls to agents for insurance quotes
summary: A caller requested a homeowners insurance quote and was offered a transfer to an agent. The call was cut off before the transfer could be completed, requiring a follow-up.
